# Vercel AI with Solana Example

## Setup

Copy the `.env.template` and populate with your values.

```
cp .env.template .env
```

## Usage

### Start TEE Simulator

```
docker pull phalanetwork/tappd-simulator:latest
docker run -d --name tappd-simulator -p 8080:8080 phalanetwork/tappd-simulator:latest
```

### Set Environment Variables

```
TEE_MODE=LOCAL
TEE_SECRET_SALT=secret_salt
```

### Run the example

```
npx ts-node index.ts
```
